{
  "stem": "10818.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Nazis found that it didn't burn sufficiently.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was, you know, as I said, a new building, relatively new and well constructed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had a beautiful sort of flattish dome.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it-- the dome, it didn't collapse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It, it-- even though, you know-- it had strong windows, vaulted windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it didn't collapse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Nazis wanted to get rid of it all together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so they dynamited it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, they tried to dynamite it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It, it didn't collapse even then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had to, had to give it several tries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And even then, I guess, the rubble was, you know, pretty difficult to cart away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there is now a sort of a part of a municipal building there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they have recently, in the last few years, found some of the portico pillars of the, of the entrance to it and made a sort of a monument, sort of a memorial right there, you know, with a plaque and, and, and an inscription and so on.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But that was just the entrance portico.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, one reason it probably didn't collapse is because so much of it was of pink marble and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so they had to really, you know, blow it up.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And for the longest time-- I, I went back there and picked up a little stone, or a little part of it, which I kept for the longest time as a memento.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I may still have it someplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because we were very much attached to it, and it was, it was-- there was a certain splendor to it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a certain splendor to the whole life.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
